e if the leadership insight gleaned is still relevant in the world today  This year s conference will provide a forum for cadets to discuss the themes of Washington s life including honor  leadership  public service and self improvement  Such discussions enhance the leadership training system of VMI  allowing cadets to reflect on their own philosophies and skills while examining those of others  Note to Cadets  Uniform for the conference is class dyke  VMI Foundation Keydet Club Alumni Webcams Directories My VMI  RESOURCES   Title IX  Health   Safety   IT   Site Index Parents   Families   Cadets   Non discrimination Statement   Privacy   THE VMI PHILOSOPHY The VMI experience is framed by relevant education within a military environment  It s an education that develops character  fosters a lifelong appreciation of physical fitness engenders a sense of responsibility to others  and cultivates the ability to master adversity  VIRGINIA MILITARY INSTITUTE Lexington  Virginia 24450 General Information   540  464 7230  Admissions  admissions vmi edu 